{"total_count":16620,"incomplete_results":false,"items":[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/issues/93849","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/issues/93849/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/issues/93849/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/issues/93849/events","html_url":"https://github.com/vercel/next.js/issues/93849","id":4446477939,"node_id":"I_kwDOBC3Cis8AAAABCQfecw","number":93849,"title":"Turbopack + Vercel: hashed pino external alias is not resolvable at runtime","user":{"login":"yayoi111","id":62744029,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYyNzQ0MDI5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/62744029?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111","html_url":"https://github.com/yayoi111","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yayoi111/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":5907879217,"node_id":"LA_kwDOBC3Cis8AAAABYCMVMQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/labels/invalid%20link","name":"invalid link","color":"444444","default":false,"description":"The issue was auto-closed due to a missing/invalid reproduction link. A new issue should be opened."}],"state":"closed","locked":true,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2026-05-14T13:55:23Z","updated_at":"2026-05-14T13:55:55Z","closed_at":"2026-05-14T13:55:50Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"NONE","issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### Link to the code that reproduces this issue\n\nI don't have a minimal reproduction yet, but this is happening in a production app deployed to Vercel.\n\n### To Reproduce\n\n1. Use Next.js 16.2.6 with the default `next build` command, which uses Turbopack in Next.js 16.\n2. Use `pino` from server-side code.\n3. Deploy to Vercel.\n4. Visit a server-rendered route that imports the server logger.\n\n### Current vs. Expected behavior\n\n#### Current behavior\n\nThe Vercel deployment fails at runtime with a hashed external module name generated by Turbopack:\n\n```text\nError: Failed to load external module pino-2e79642258e38174:\nError: Cannot find module 'pino-2e79642258e38174'\nRequire stack:\n- /var/task/.next/server/chunks/ssr/[root-of-the-server]__0c3ufd7._.js\n- /var/task/.next/server/chunks/ssr/[turbopack]_runtime.js\n- /var/task/.next/server/app/(authenticated)/(org-selected)/(subscription)/todo/page.js\n- /var/task/node_modules/.pnpm/next@16.2.6_.../node_modules/next/dist/compiled/next-server/server.runtime.prod.js\n- /var/task/___next_launcher.cjs\n- /opt/rust/nodejs.js\n```\n\nThe generated server chunk contains:\n\n```js\nrequire(\"pino-2e79642258e38174\")\n```\n\nIn the local build output, `.next/node_modules` contains a symlink for that alias:\n\n```text\n.next/node_modules/pino-2e79642258e38174 -> ../../node_modules/.pnpm/pino@10.3.1/node_modules/pino\n```\n\nSo the alias exists locally, but it does not appear to be resolvable inside the Vercel serverless runtime artifact.\n\n#### Expected behavior\n\nThe Vercel runtime should be able to resolve the externalized `pino` package, or Turbopack should emit a runtime-resolvable external reference.\n\n### Environment\n\n```text\nNext.js: 16.2.6\nReact: 19.2.4\nNode: 22.x on Vercel\nPackage manager: pnpm\nBundler: Turbopack via default `next build`\nDeployment: Vercel Serverless\npino: 10.3.1\n```\n\nRelevant `next.config.ts`:\n\n```ts\nconst nextConfig = {\n  serverExternalPackages: [\"pino\"],\n};\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\nThis seems related to, but not exactly the same as, the original `Cannot find module './transport-stream'` issue discussed in:\n\n- https://github.com/vercel/next.js/issues/86099\n- https://github.com/vercel/next.js/issues/87342\n- https://github.com/vercel/next.js/issues/89851\n\nPR https://github.com/vercel/next.js/pull/86884 added pino-related packages to the automatic `serverExternalPackages` list, but this failure mode is different: the package is externalized, yet the generated hashed alias `pino-<hash>` is not resolvable at runtime on Vercel.\n\n### Workaround\n\nBuilding with Webpack avoids the issue:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"next build --webpack\"\n  }\n}\n```","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/issues/93849/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/issues/93849/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/intelseclab/poc-archive/issues/56","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/intelseclab/poc-archive","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/intelseclab/poc-archive/issues/56/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/intelseclab/poc-archive/issues/56/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/intelseclab/poc-archive/issues/56/events","html_url":"https://github.com/intelseclab/poc-archive/issues/56","id":4460326377,"node_id":"I_kwDOSdTm2c8AAAABCdst6Q","number":56,"tit