mmunication with the Next.js upstream community.\n\n### Evidence of React ecosystem relevance\n\n1. natively react support : https://utoo.land/en/docs/utoopack/config#react\n2. in-browser toolchain, directly install deps, building react app with postcss and tailwindcss support: https://utoo-repl.vercel.app/\n3. contributions to next.js and Turbopack: https://github.com/search?q=repo%3Avercel%2Fnext.js%20is%3Apr%20is%3Amerged%20author%3Afireairforce%20author%3Axusd320&type=pullrequests\n\n### Non-goals\n\n_No response_","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/react-foundation-dev/react.foundation/issues/58/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":1},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/react-foundation-dev/react.foundation/issues/58/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/cloudflare/vinext/issues/1007","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/cloudflare/vinext","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/cloudflare/vinext/issues/1007/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/cloudflare/vinext/issues/1007/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/cloudflare/vinext/issues/1007/events","html_url":"https://github.com/cloudflare/vinext/issues/1007","id":4366959710,"node_id":"I_kwDORXYnQM8AAAABBEqEXg","number":1007,"title":"next/image: hydration-level onError replay via useLayoutEffect","user":{"login":"Divkix","id":23524935,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIzNTI0OTM1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23524935?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix","html_url":"https://github.com/Divkix","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Divkix/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2026-05-01T22:34:48Z","updated_at":"2026-05-02T23:12:28Z","closed_at":"2026-05-02T23:12:28Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Identified during review of #1004.\n\n## Context\nThe upstream Next.js PR (https://github.com/vercel/next.js/pull/93209) uses a `useLayoutEffect` + `img.src = img.src` pattern to replay error events that are lost before React hydration completes. The vinext implementation in #1004 uses a simpler `useRef`-based dedup that doesn't handle this case.\n\n## Impact\nImages that fail to load *before* React hydration completes (e.g., during SSR streaming or initial HTML parse) won't fire `onError` callbacks. This means error state management in parent components won't trigger for pre-hydration failures.\n\n## Suggested approach\nAdd a `useLayoutEffect` that, when `onError` is provided, sets `img.src = img.src` on the ref to re-trigger the load/error cycle after hydration. This mirrors the upstream Next.js fix in vercel/next.js#93209.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/cloudflare/vinext/issues/1007/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/cloudflare/vin