--\n\n## Showcase\n\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\">\n      <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/94b92c29-9313-41e2-94ad-7a2dcb8be095\" alt=\"냉장고 재료 관리\" />\n      <br />\n      <sub><b>냉장고 재료 관리</b><br />보유한 재료로 레시피를 탐색</sub>\n    </td>\n    <td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\">\n      <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3f3c350a-46a8-4d73-aa21-35831c77e824\" alt=\"개인화 데이터\" />\n      <br />\n      <sub><b>개인화</b><br />알레르기·취향을 반영한 추천</sub>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\">\n      <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/455ac18e-093a-444e-9533-e78dff4af144\" alt=\"AI 레시피 생성\" />\n      <br />\n      <sub><b>AI 레시피 생성</b><br />선택한 모델로 맞춤형 레시피</sub>\n    </td>\n    <td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\">\n      <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3f3c350a-46a8-4d73-aa21-35831c77e824\" alt=\"공유\" />\n      <br />\n      <sub><b>공유 & 레시피북</b><br />컬렉션으로 모으고 나누기</sub>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br />\n\n## Features\n\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\">\n      <h3>AI 레시피 생성</h3>\n      <p>영양 · 재료 · 파인다이닝 · 가성비 <b>4가지 모드</b>로 LLM 호출. Vercel AI SDK 기반 스트리밍.</p>\n    </td>\n    <td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\">\n      <h3>유튜브 레시피 임포트</h3>\n      <p>유튜브 URL 한 줄로 레시피 카드 자동 생성. 트렌딩 큐레이션과 쿼터 관리 내장.</p>\n    </td>\n    <td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\">\n      <h3>냉장고 재료 관리</h3>\n      <p>보유 재료를 등록하고 그 안에서만 가능한 레시피를 탐색. 유통기한 추적.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\">\n      <h3>레시피북 & 캘린더</h3>\n      <p>레시피를 컬렉션으로 묶고, 캘린더에 요리한 날을 기록. 타임라인 회고.</p>\n    </td>\n    <td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\">\n      <h3>검색 & 필터</h3>\n      <p>재료 · 정렬 · 태그 · 요리 타입 4축 복합 필터. 큐레이션 기반 디스커버리.</p>\n    </td>\n    <td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\">\n      <h3>소셜 로그인</h3>\n      <p>Google · Apple · Kakao · Naver 4종 OAuth. WebView에서 네이티브 인증 브리지.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br />\n\n## Architecture\n\nNext.js 15 웹과 React Native WebView 앱(iOS/Android)이 **같은 코드베이스**를 공유합니다.\n네이티브 기능(햅틱, 푸시, 공유, 인증)은 WebView Bridge로 노출됩니다.\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    subgraph Client\n        Web[\"Next.js 15<br/>App Router · RSC\"]\n        Bridge[\"WebView Bridge<br/>haptic · auth · share · push\"]\n        RN[\"React Native Shell<br/>iOS · Android\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Backend\n        API[(Recipe API)]\n        AI[\"Vercel AI SDK<br/>OpenAI\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Observability\n        Sentry\n        PostHog\n    end\n\n    Web <--> Bridge\n    Bridge <--> RN\n    Web --> API\n    Web --> AI\n    Web -.-> Sentry\n    Web -.-> PostHog\n```\n\n**Feature-Sliced Design** 4단계 구조 (`shared → entities → features → widgets → app`).\n역방향 import 금지, 동일 레이어 cross-import 금지.\n\n<sub>entities <b>7</b> · features <b>48</b> · widgets <b>45</b> · routes <b>20+</b></sub>\n\n<br />\n\n## Built with\n\n<p>\n  <img src=\"https://skillicons.dev/icons?i=nextjs,react,typescript,tailwind,vercel\" />\n  <img src=\"https://skillicons.dev/icons?i=nodejs,vite,jest,sentry,figma\" />\n</p>\n\n| Layer | Tech |\n|---|---|\n| **Framework** | Next.js 15.3 (App Router · Turbopack) · React 19 |\n| **Language** | TypeScript 5 (strict) |\n| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS 4 · Radix UI |\n| **Animation** | Motion 12 · GSAP 3 |\n| **State** | TanStack Query 5 · Zustand 5 |\n| **Forms** | React Hook Form 7 · Zod 4 |\n| **AI** | Vercel AI SDK 5 · OpenAI |\n| **Observability** | Sentry · PostHog · Lighthouse CI |\n| **Compiler** | React Compiler (experimental) |\n\n<br />\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <sub>Made with 🍳 by <a href=\"https://github.com/1119wj\">@1119wj</a></sub>\n</div>\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Haemeok/Capstone-frontend/issues/120/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Haemeok/Capstone-frontend/issues/120/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"complete